title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 ยง 297.5 - Time and place for filing City of New York earnings tax returns and payment of City of New York earnings tax
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 ยง 297.5 - Time and place for filing City of New York earnings tax returns and payment of City of New York earnings tax

State Regulations

Administrative Code of the City of New York, ยง
11-1917

The provisions of Part 152 of this Title, with respect to
the time and place for filing New York State income tax returns and payment of

New York State income tax, shall also be applicable to the time and place for
filing City of New York earnings tax returns and payment of City of New York
earnings tax. Also see sections
297.1
and
297.2
of this Title, respectively, with respect to combined returns and payment of a
single amount to the commissioner. Notes
